        "tab_Eh7cBq": {
          "type": "tab",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Delivery and payment",
            "id": "delivery",
            "html": "<p><strong>📦 Delivery and Payment</strong></p>\n\n<p>All EVA mats are made to order from scratch, with attention to detail and a perfect fit for your specific car model.</p>\n\n<p style=\"border:1px solid #ef022d; padding:10px; border-radius:8px;\">💡 The current standard order processing time is 14 business days.</p>\n\n<p>Choose the production speed of your order</p>\n\n<p>Each set of mats is made individually, so you can decide how quickly your order enters production.</p>\n\n<p>Available production options:</p>\n\n<p>🟢 Standard - 14 business days<br>\nProcessed in the standard production queue.</p>\n\n<p>🟠 Express - 7 business days<br>\nHigher priority in the production queue.</p>\n\n<p>Once production is completed, the mats are immediately prepared for shipment.</p>\n\n<p>You can choose the priority production option on the “Delivery and Payment” page when selecting the delivery method. The Express service is available at an additional cost.</p>\n\n<p>🚗 We do our best to process orders as quickly as possible. However, during periods of increased order volume, such as seasonal peaks, promotions, or holidays, processing times may be extended.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Delivery methods:</strong></p>\n\n<div class=\"product_tabs__containers_item_block\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/Frame_427319187.svg?v=1754576315\" alt=\"InPost\"> \n  <ul>\n    <li>InPost Courier (online payment or cash on delivery)</li>\n    <li>InPost Parcel Locker (online payment only)</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"product_tabs__containers_item_block\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/dpd.svg?v=1754574037\" alt=\"DPD\"> \n  <ul>\n    <li>DPD Courier (online payment or cash on delivery)</li>\n    <li>DPD Pickup Point (online payment only)</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"product_tabs__containers_item_block\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0790/9218/7414/files/GLS_Logo_2021_svg.svg?v=1774966899\" alt=\"GLS\"> \n  <ul>\n    <li>GLS Courier (online payment or cash on delivery)</li>\n    <li>GLS Parcel Shop (online payment only)</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n<p><strong>Online payments:</strong></p>\n\n<ul class=\"evamats-footer__payment-list list-unstyled\">\n  <li class=\"evamats-footer__payment-item\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/przelewy24_logo_svg.svg?v=1754575627\" alt=\"Przelewy24\">\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"evamats-footer__payment-item\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/blik_9f0af63c-fe50-41e4-9eed-8eba66188150.svg?v=1754574036\" alt=\"BLIK\">\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"evamats-footer__payment-item\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/PayPo_logo_kolor.svg?v=1754574985\" alt=\"PayPo\">\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"evamats-footer__payment-item\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/visa_f5353cf6-3937-47e8-b0d0-4dffa5d38d04.svg?v=1754574037\" alt=\"Visa\">\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"evamats-footer__payment-item\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/mc_e03f8da5-c6a9-4429-bc4f-800d875497b5.svg?v=1754574036\" alt=\"Mastercard\">\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"evamats-footer__payment-item\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/apay_01efa87d-bab1-4df5-8583-9bd84c0efe6c.svg?v=1754575856\" alt=\"Apple Pay\">\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"evamats-footer__payment-item\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0734/7988/1010/files/gpay_763ff9ab-ac05-4efa-ae2a-34b490f1dbc2.svg?v=1754574037\" alt=\"Google Pay\">\n  </li>\n<p></p>\n\n<p><strong>Safe shopping:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Encrypted payments</li>\n  <li>Reliable logistics</li>\n  <li>Ongoing customer support</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Thank you for choosing a Polish-made product designed with quality and functionality in mind. Driver satisfaction is our top priority.</p>\n</ul>"
